  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Clinical research of Yang Yin Fu Zheng Jie Du therapy in HBV related hepatocellular carcinoma&#xD;
      induced anemia. The purpose of this study is to observe the efficacy of routine medical care&#xD;
      combined with Yang Yin Fu Zheng Jie Du therapy for patients belong to HBV-HCC induced anemia.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
